":165470,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無話好唔好既<br />\n純粹講緊一個困難模式一個普通<br />\n<br />\n講真有得選擇既邊個想玩困？係呀係無大志架啦<br />\n你地咁有大志咪係香港慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做隻狗都係食訓屙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗做咁多野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人一世，過得開心咪得咯<br />\n先天下之憂而憂咩？憂唔憂你咪又係食物鏈底層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣起碼好過香港，玩既地方多工種多，食住行都好過香港<br />\n香港係連個狗竇都要等主人施捨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16b279fa1bce846c85ea12103812370422f503a","tid":165470,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"人哋起碼唔使俾人釋法 <br />\n同每日150個汚染物洗港"},{"pid":"c340725cfa6e1652e544620a058b6fe3b1a2d1d2","tid":165470,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人哋起碼唔使俾人釋法 <br />\n同每日150個汚染物洗港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未計150個再繁殖既後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}